Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.59,0:24:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是和她戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.99,0:24:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要正當化嗎  把這行為
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還太早
